<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>EC-30 ABS / ATC CONTROLLER - EC-30 HARDWARE CONFIGURATIONS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>EC-30 HARDWARE CONFIGURATIONS</title>
        <para>The EC-30 ABS ECU is available in different hardware configurations in order to support various ABS, ATC
            and power line carrier (PLC) features. See
            <hotlnk xrefid="t0404303">Table 3</hotlnk>.
        </para>
        <para>EC-30 premium PLC hardware can be configured for four or six sensors, with or without ATC, and PLC can be
            disabled.
        </para>
        <para>EC-30 basic models can not be configured for six sensors or ATC.</para>
        <para>PLC hardware is needed to support PLC communication.</para>
        <para>Always verify that you are working with the correct EC-30 by referring to the part number label on the
            ECU.
        </para>
